#: ../base/ufos/tips.ufo:7
msgid ""
"With multiplayer teams, make sure your best soldiers are at the top of the "
"team list. When the soldier limit is lower than the amount of soldiers in your "
"team, the soldiers at the top of the list will be used for the game."
